    "description": [
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "  CH.05 · THE WIZARD'S TABLE",
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "",
      "▸ Iron's Spellbooks Wizard mobs are the main source",
      "  of rare spell scrolls and spell-crafting materials.",
      "  The Wizard's Table scroll drops from them directly.",
      "  Read it. Then find them.",
      "",
      "◈ ISS WIZARD MOB",
      "  └ Spawns in: witch huts, mage towers,",
      "    wizard camp structures (night spawns)",
      "  └ Drops: dacxirons scroll (12%),",
      "    random spell scrolls, mana-related items",
      "  └ ▲ Wizards cast active spells — dodge their AoE",
      "  └ ISS Wizard ≠ vanilla Witch (separate mob)",
      "",
      "◈ ARCANE WORKTABLE",
      "  └ Crafts specific spells from components",
      "  └ Allows upgrading spell level (I → II → III)",
      "  └ Requires: mana crystals + school-specific materials",
      "  └ T.O Magic 'n Extras (traveloptics namespace)",
      "    is an ISS addon — adds additional items",
      "",
      "◈ SCROLL: The Wizard's Table",
      "  └ Found in: ISS Wizard drops (12%),",
      "    wizard tower loot, arcane workshop ruins",
      "  └ Research time: 20 min",
      "  └ Unlocks: arcane worktable system, ISS Wizard awareness,",
      "    spell upgrading knowledge",
      "",
      "▸ The scroll was written by a wizard",
      "  explaining to non-wizards how wizards think.",
      "  It is more useful to non-wizards than to wizards.",
      "  The wizard knew that.",
      "",
      "▶ Find The Wizard's Table scroll [check]",
      "▶ Craft or find an Arcane Worktable [check]",
      "",
      "◇ Spell Schools scroll (Ch09) covers the full",
      "  casting system — mana, scaling, combat integration.",
      "  The Wizard's Table is the workshop.",
      "  The School is the curriculum."
    ],
